See also: 訓詁學
Chinese[edit]



to interpret the meaning of characters, words and phrases in Classical Chinese texts

 
learn; study; science
learn; study; science; -ology




trad. (訓詁學)
訓詁
學


simp. (訓詁學)
訓詁
學


